{"word":"Ezra","slug":"ezra","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ezra</b> <a href=\"#/H5830\">H5830</a><br/><a href=\"#/H5831\">H5831</a> <br/> 1. A famous scribe and priest<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=6'>Ezr 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=10'>Ezr 7:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=21'>Ezr 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=36'>Neh 12:36</a> <br/> - Appoints a fast<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=21'>Ezr 8:21</a> <br/> - Commissioned by Artaxerxes, returns to Jerusalem with a large company of Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=8'>Ezr 7:8</a> <br/> - His charge to the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=29'>Ezr 8:29</a> <br/> - Exhorts people to put away their heathen wives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=15'>Ezr 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=17'>Ezr 10:17</a> <br/> - Reads the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8'>Neh 8</a> <br/> - Reforms corruptions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10'>Ezr 10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13'>Neh 13</a> <br/> - Dedicates the wall of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=43'>Neh 12:43</a> <br/> 2. A leading priest among the colonists under Zerubbabel<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=1'>Neh 12:1</a> <br/> - Probably identical with Azariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=2'>Neh 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=1'>Ezr 7:1</a> <br/> 3. A descendant of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=17'>1Ch 4:17</a>"}]}